 # Vedic AI: Integrating Ancient Wisdom with Artificial Intelligence  

This project explores **Vedic epistemology, Dharma ethics, and Nyaya logic** in AI models to create a self-regulating intelligence based on **Rta (Cosmic Order)**.  

## Key Features:
- **Nyaya-based logical reasoning in AI.**  
- **Dharma-driven ethical self-regulation.**  
- **Vedic-inspired deep learning architecture.**  
- **AI consciousness modeling using Vedantic principles.**  

## Installation
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/vedic-ai-project.git
cd vedic-ai-project
pip install -r requirements.txt
